            HYPE PERFORMANCE AND RECOVERY CLUB - L.L.C - S.P.C ("HYPE Club", "we" or "us"), takes the privacy of your information very seriously. This privacy policy describes how HYPE Club shall collect and use your personal data, including the personal information we receive from you ("you" or "your") in the course of our business. This privacy policy applies to our use of any and all data collected by us or provided by you in relation to your use of our website www.hypeclub.com ("Website").
