                <span style="position: absolute; left: 0; color: {{ accent_color }};">•</span>
                This privacy policy applies only to the actions of HYPE Club and you with respect to this Website. It does not extend to any websites that can be accessed from this Website including, but not limited to, any links we may provide to social media websites.
